{"word":"G5269 - ὑποζώννυμι - hypozṓnnymi - hoop-od-zone'-noo-mee - Undergirt","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑποζώννυμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypozṓnnymi</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-od-zone'-noo-mee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Undergirt</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சுற்றிக் கட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to under - gird"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5259 - ὑπό - hypó - hoop-o'/5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G2224 - ζώννυμι - zṓnnymi - dzone'-noo-mi/2224\">G2224</a>; to <i>gird under</i>, that is, <i>frap</i> (a vessel with cables across the keel, sides and deck): - undergirt.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}